'''Juan Ismael Calzada'''<ref>[http://asaweb.huh.harvard.edu:8080/databases/botanists?id=137295 HUH - Databases - Botanist Search Results]   {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5vBMrNS9j?url=http://asaweb.huh.harvard.edu:8080/databases/botanists?id=137295 |date=December 23, 2010 }}</ref> is a Mexican botanist and collector. Dr  Calzada is credited with the discovery of the elm ''[[Ulmus ismaelis]]'', named in his honour.

